data.description: Available again!!!! This SPACIOUS & UPDATED townhome has all the room, features, and location to everything you could possibly need!!! Qualifies for all financing types!!! This 4 bed, 3 bath townhome has a variety of fantastic exterior features such as attached 1-car garage, private courtyard with a large exterior storage shed & rear screened-in lanai, overlooking peaceful landscaped area. Step inside to a well-appointed home featuring recently-remodeled kitchen sporting new cabinets, appliances, lighting, granite counters, tiled backslash, & under-sink R.O. system!!! Bathrooms have been recently remodeled as well, with upgraded vanities/counters & fully-tiled stalls. New entry doors have recently been installed. All electrical outlets have been replaced. Indoor laundry room, with newer stackable washer/dryer! Plenty of storage, both in closet space, but also this home features sizable under-stair storage as well! Be in one of the best locations of Fort Myers, a 30-second drive to Publix, CVS Pharmacy, and the South Cape Bridge, and only minutes to shopping, fine dining, and entertainment by way of Bell Tower Shops, the Downtown River District and more. Schedule your showing today!
